      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Montrer que la série de terme général $\\Arctan(n+a) - \\Arctan n$ est\n    convergente.",
        "html": "<p>Montrer que la série de terme général <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\Arctan(n+a) - \\Arctan n\\)</span> est\nconvergente.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "ea6f4719-9007-491e-b341-1cc79c285891",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$\\sim \\frac a{n^2}$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\sim \\frac a{n^2}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "98b405ae-8770-4bf2-a462-88231fd43d52",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "On pose $S(a) = \\sum_{k=0}^\\infty (\\Arctan(k+a) - \\Arctan k)$.\n    Trouver $\\lim_{a\\to+\\infty} S(a)$.",
        "html": "<p>On pose <span class=\"math inline\">\\(S(a) = \\sum_{k=0}^\\infty\n(\\Arctan(k+a) - \\Arctan k)\\)</span>. Trouver <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\lim_{a\\to+\\infty} S(a)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "2ccc0e5e-c274-4482-ad2e-aba89e786ce1",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$S(a) \\ge \\sum_{k=0}^n \\Arctan(k+a)-\\Arctan k \\to\n              \\frac\\pi2 + \\Arctan 1 + \\Arctan\\frac12 + \\dots\n              + \\Arctan\\frac1n\n               \\Rightarrow  S(a) \\to +\\infty$ lorsque $a\\to+\\infty$ .",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(S(a) \\ge \\sum_{k=0}^n\n\\Arctan(k+a)-\\Arctan k \\to\n              \\frac\\pi2 + \\Arctan 1 + \\Arctan\\frac12 + \\dots\n              + \\Arctan\\frac1n\n               \\Rightarrow  S(a) \\to +\\infty\\)</span> lorsque <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(a\\to+\\infty\\)</span> .</p>\n"
      }
    }
  ],
